OL,3,CNext government 'will need to raise
OL,4,Ctaxes to maintain public services'
OL,6,FThe winner of the next general
OL,7,Felection will have to raise taxes to
OL,8,Fmaintain the current provision for
OL,9,Fpublic services, according to new
OL,10,Fanalysis by a leading think tank.
OL,12,FThe National Institute of Economic and
OL,13,FSocial Research (NIESR) added that
OL,14,Fthere is "essentially no fiscal
OL,15,Fheadroom for any further tax cuts"
OL,16,Famid slow economic growth and easing
OL,17,Finflation.
