OL,3,CNext government 'will need to raise
OL,4,Ctaxes to maintain public services'
OL,6,FIt comes a week after the UK's
OL,7,Feconomic growth prospects were
OL,8,Fdowngraded for the next two years by
OL,9,Fthe Organisation for Economic Co-
OL,10,Foperation and Development (OECD),
OL,11,Fadding that it is on track for the
OL,12,Fweakest growth of the G7 group of
OL,13,Fcountries next year.
OL,15,FStephen Millard, deputy director for
OL,16,Fmacroeconomic modelling and
OL,17,Fforecasting at NIESR, said: "Despite
OL,18,Fthe welcome fall in inflation, UK
OL,19,Fgrowth remains anaemic.
