OL,3,CNext government 'will need to raise
OL,4,Ctaxes to maintain public services'
OL,6,F"This will make it difficult for any
OL,7,Fincoming government to carry out the
OL,8,Fmuch-needed investment in
OL,9,Finfrastructure and the green
OL,10,Ftransition, as well as increase
OL,11,Fspending on public services and
OL,12,Fdefence, without either raising taxes
OL,13,For rewriting the fiscal rules.
OL,15,F"This makes clear the need to reform
OL,16,Fthe fiscal framework to enable the
OL,17,Fgovernment to do what is needed for
OL,18,Fthe economy in a fiscally sustainable
OL,19,Fway."
