OL,3,CNext government 'will need to raise
OL,4,Ctaxes to maintain public services'
OL,6,FIt is currently widely expected that
OL,7,Fthe next UK general election will take
OL,8,Fplace in the second half of 2024, with
OL,9,Fthe Labour Party shadow chancellor
OL,10,FRachel Reeves saying earlier this week
OL,11,Fthat they plan to fight the next
OL,12,Felection on the state of the economy.
OL,14,FNIESR also said in the report that it
OL,15,Fpredicts there will next be an
OL,16,Finterest rate cut, from the current
OL,17,Flevel of 5.25%, in August. It has
OL,18,Ffactored in two cuts this year.
