OL,4,Ctaxes to maintain public services'
OL,6,FThe forecasts also indicated that
OL,7,Faverage living standards are due to
OL,8,Fimprove by around 6% in 2024/25
OL,9,Fcompared with the previous year, but
OL,10,Fstressed this picture varies
OL,11,Fsignificantly between the income
OL,12,Fdistribution.
OL,14,FThe poorest tenth of households will
OL,15,Fexperience a 2% decline in disposable
OL,16,Fincome, while households in deciles
OL,17,Ffour to nine will see a 7%-8%
OL,18,Fimprovement.
